OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine warm
OL,6,Fsunny evening in all areas then a dry
OL,7,Fnight with some long clear spells.
OL,8,FClouding over over the Eastern Borders
OL,9,Fand East Lothians by morning.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSaturday:FA dry day. A sunny start in
OL,12,Fwest but cloudy in the east. Cloud
OL,13,Fclearing the east through the morning
OL,14,Fto leave good sunny spells across the
OL,15,Fregion.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FIt will
OL,18,Fbe a dry few days with variable cloud
OL,19,Fand some sunny spells. Mainly light
OL,20,Fwinds, and on the warm side.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
